(0) READ-ITEM A
(1) COMPARE A(0) WITH A(1) ; IF LESS GO TO OPERATION 5
(2) TRANSFER A(0) TO TEMP
(3) TRANSFER A(1) TO A(0)
(4) TRANSFER TEMP TO A(1)
(5) COMPARE A(1) WITH A(2) ; IF LESS GO TO OPERATION 9
(6) TRANSFER A(1) TO TEMP
(7) TRANSFER A(2) TO A(1)
(8) TRANSFER TEMP TO A(2)
(9) COMPARE A(2) WITH A(3) ; IF LESS GO TO OPERATION 13
(10) TRANSFER A(2) TO TEMP
(11) TRANSFER A(3) TO A(2)
(12) TRANSFER TEMP TO A(3)
(13) COMPARE A(3) WITH A(4) ; IF LESS GO TO OPERATION 17
(14) TRANSFER A(3) TO TEMP
(15) TRANSFER A(4) TO A(3)
(16) TRANSFER TEMP TO A(4)
(17) WRITE-ITEM A
(18) STOP
